the words ``Direct Loans'' in paragraph (b)(1)(x); by adding the words ``or Federal'' before the word ``PLUS'', by
removing the comma after the words ``PLUS loan'', and by removing the words ``or non-need-based ICL'' before the word
``as'' in paragraph (b)(3); and by revising paragraphs (c) introductory text, (c)(1), (c)(2), and (c)(3) to read
as follows: 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=80 g=1 f=1 -->
&sect;676.14
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=89 g=1 f=1 -->
